    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Rcpp and Expression Templates]]></title>
    <link href="http://nathan-russell-blog.github.io/blog/2015/11/21/rcpp-and-expression-templates/"/>
    <updated>2015-11-21T19:58:22-05:00</updated>
